  "prompt": "Which is the best whirlpool washing machine service center in Hyderabad?",
  "response": "I don't have real-time data, but I can suggest ways to find the best Whirlpool washing machine service center in Hyderabad:\n\n1. **Official Whirlpool Service Center**: The most reliable option is to contact Whirlpool's official customer service. They can direct you to authorized service centers in Hyderabad. You can typically find this information on Whirlpool's official website.\n\n2. **Online Reviews**: Check platforms like Google Reviews or Justdial for customer feedback on various service centers in Hyderabad. Look for those with high ratings and positive reviews.\n\n3. **Local Directories**: Websites like Sulekha and UrbanClap often list service centers with customer ratings, which can help you decide.\n\n4. **Word of Mouth**: Ask friends, family, or neighbors for recommendations. Personal experiences can be very telling in terms of reliability and quality of service.\n\n5. **Social Media**: Post a query on local Facebook groups or other social media platforms dedicated to Hyderabad consumers. Community members often share their experiences and can recommend good service centers. \n\nMake sure to verify any service center's credentials and warranty terms before availing of their services.",
